snippet.textDisplay: I've been raising chickens, quails, turkeys, and ducks for years. Online sources will tell you "DoNt ToUcH ThE ChIcKs. YoU'Ll KiLl tHeM!!" But I'm here to tell you. Quails actually like attention. So go ahead and hold your children
